    <string name="sliders_2_paragraph_1">First you\'ll need to authorize our mail server to send to your kindle device the manga documents:</string>
    <string name="sliders_2_paragraph_2">You can do that from your Amazon\'s Account, search for \"Manage your Content and Devices\" and go to \"Preferences\".</string>
